mlx5e_netdev_change_profile+0x44/0x138 [mlx5_core]
mlx5e_netdev_attach_nic_profile+0x28/0x38 [mlx5_core]
mlx5e_vport_rep_unload+0x184/0x1b8 [mlx5_core]
